{"id":140784,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/03/图辑：英国20年来超级大明月/","date":"2011-03-21T09:30:27Z","modified":"2011-03-21T09:30:27Z","title":"图辑：英国20年来超级大明月","content":"<div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div><a href=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2011/03/20/110320215456_moon1_926x521_bbc_nocredit.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"英国超级大明月\" height=\"60\" src=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/ic/106x60/www.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2011/03/20/110320215456_moon1_926x521_bbc_nocredit.jpg\" width=\"106\" /></a></div>\n<div>英国在3月19日迎来近20年来最大最明的月亮。这一天，月亮距离地球的距离是20年来最近的。各地网友给BBC发来他们镜头下的月色。Sumit Kimar摄于格拉斯哥</div>\n</p></div>\n</p></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div><a href=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2011/03/20/110320215706_moon2_926x521_bbc_nocredit.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"英国超级大明月\" height=\"60\" src=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/ic/106x60/www.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2011/03/20/110320215706_moon2_926x521_bbc_nocredit.jpg\" width=\"106\" /></a></div>\n<div>由于月球轨道成椭圆形，所以即便同是十五的月亮，大小也是不同的。Jerry Tye摄于萨福克</div>\n</p></div>\n</p></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div><a href=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2011/03/20/110320215824_moon3_926x521_bbc_nocredit.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"英国超级大明月\" height=\"60\" src=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/ic/106x60/www.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2011/03/20/110320215824_moon3_926x521_bbc_nocredit.jpg\" width=\"106\" /></a></div>\n<div>超级明月在当天离地球的距离近了31000英里，所以看起来比平时大了14%。Matthew Ormesher摄于梅西塞德</div>\n</p></div>\n</p></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div><a href=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2011/03/20/110320215920_moon4_926x521_bbc_nocredit.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"英国超级大明月\" height=\"60\" src=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/ic/106x60/www.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2011/03/20/110320215920_moon4_926x521_bbc_nocredit.jpg\" width=\"106\" /></a></div>\n<div>好天气使伦敦人也能欣赏到这难得的月色。Claire Massingham摄于伦敦</div>\n</p></div>\n</p></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div><a href=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2011/03/20/110320220018_moon5_926x521_bbc_nocredit.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"英国超级大明月\" height=\"60\" src=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/ic/106x60/www.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2011/03/20/110320220018_moon5_926x521_bbc_nocredit.jpg\" width=\"106\" /></a></div>\n<div>从肯特郡看海上的超级明月。James Root 摄于肯特郡</div>\n</p></div>\n</p></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div><a href=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2011/03/20/110320220119_moon6_926x521_bbc_nocredit.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"英国超级大明月\" height=\"60\" src=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/ic/106x60/www.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2011/03/20/110320220119_moon6_926x521_bbc_nocredit.jpg\" width=\"106\" /></a></div>\n<div>超级大明月比往日的亮度也高出三成。这是从多塞特看怀特岛上的明月。Brian Dempsey摄于多塞特</div>\n</p></div>\n</p></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div><a href=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2011/03/20/110320220211_moon7_926x521_bbc_nocredit.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"英国超级大明月\" height=\"60\" src=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/ic/106x60/www.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2011/03/20/110320220211_moon7_926x521_bbc_nocredit.jpg\" width=\"106\" /></a></div>\n<div>牛津郡看到的月亮。Mandalika Bhattacharya摄于牛津郡</div>\n</p></div>\n</p></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div><a href=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2011/03/20/110320220310_moon8_926x521_bbc_nocredit.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"英国超级大明月\" height=\"60\" src=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/ic/106x60/www.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2011/03/20/110320220310_moon8_926x521_bbc_nocredit.jpg\" width=\"106\" /></a></div>\n<div>超级大明月能引起更大的潮水，但并不会引发任何自然灾害。Martin Thome 拍下了月亮落入海平面前的美景。</div>\n</p></div>\n</p></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div><a href=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2011/03/20/110320220446_moon9_926x521_bbc_nocredit.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"英国超级大明月\" height=\"60\" src=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/ic/106x60/www.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2011/03/20/110320220446_moon9_926x521_bbc_nocredit.jpg\" width=\"106\" /></a></div>\n<div>如果19日晚上你错过了这一超级大明月，再等约20年你将有机会欣赏到同样的美景。Ali Napier摄于珀斯郡</div>\n</p></div>\n</p></div>\n</li>\n</ul></div>\n</p></div>\n</p></div>\n</p></div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/J2O67teCMO2hYoJLsip8kH3k6Ew/0/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/J2O67teCMO2hYoJLsip8kH3k6Ew/0/di\"></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/J2O67teCMO2hYoJLsip8kH3k6Ew/1/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/J2O67teCMO2hYoJLsip8kH3k6Ew/1/di\"></a></p>\n<p><img height=\"1\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/cnbbc/~4/__ct_Zl0PPs\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<p><b>要翻墙？(发邮件到Gmail):hulianwangziyouATgmail.com</b></p>\n","author":176,"categories":[8779],"tags":[]}